        When a post goes out, it goes to all four platforms. When something needs your attention, it
        surfaces to one dashboard.
      </p>

      <div class="solution-grid">
        <div class="solution-card">
          <div class="solution-icon">⚡</div>
          <h3>Live Automation Workflows</h3>
          <p>Appointment follow-ups, review requests, lead nurturing, social publishing — built once, running 24/7 for $6/month in infrastructure.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="solution-card">
          <div class="solution-icon">🔗</div>
          <h3>Everything Connected</h3>
          <p>Your website, email, CRM, social, and scheduling all talk to each other. No more copy-pasting between platforms. No more manual reports.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="solution-card">
          <div class="solution-icon">📊</div>
          <h3>One Unified Dashboard</h3>
          <p>All your metrics, alerts, bookings, and approvals in a single Slack dashboard. Your business briefs you every morning — not the other way around.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="solution-card">
          <div class="solution-icon">🌐</div>
          <h3>Built to Be Found</h3>
          <p>Mobile-first, SEO-optimized websites built in Astro — faster than WordPress, cheaper to host ($0 on Cloudflare), and designed to rank.</p>
        </div>
